-beb4-41a3-ac15-bd889f7b9e77.JPG", "/uploads/1773916705157-784dc0d5-279f-4642-829e-79060c87dca1.JPG"], "crew206Pictures": ["/uploads/1773916804398-a67df8fa-aebc-4e3b-b020-515ab2bee53d.JPG", "/uploads/1773916804552-54c9d66b-4377-4293-b42b-6826c0a7054c.JPG", "/uploads/1773916804667-e28d8276-ba71-4c35-9e5f-3982ec9203f1.JPG", "/uploads/1773916804787-b380fcd0-22b2-4a11-a842-1af21ea74c0f.JPG", "/uploads/1773916804865-b55c5983-e4d3-4b72-b82c-04d4d481962f.JPG", "/uploads/1773916804955-d11f3065-a82a-4a81-9c8e-73adad138529.JPG", "/uploads/1773916843396-ac1de8d6-a1f0-4242-8c61-1bd34fb2e976.JPG", "/uploads/1773916843578-9501adcd-4e1e-4a3d-a96b-6970e6b473eb.JPG", "/uploads/1773916843751-73d622cc-273f-4056-958a-26442b15ddb6.JPG", "/uploads/1773916843816-fe5ee7dc-bdba-487b-bf81-83e1a8a73fe5.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864441-d1015b6f-a7c4-4c6f-b75c-2440f57a88f7.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864515-48e32b38-92ed-452a-ab50-23054ed6a288.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864593-073c741b-df55-4a0d-b546-d182577ddc15.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864655-2b631da3-34c8-4c0e-8c2b-350b6071b186.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864771-c5cd666c-02ad-4ead-bad9-8b862631bfbb.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864888-95399d5a-d5b8-4ec0-b13b-2e9ce6db0838.JPG", "/uploads/1773916864976-8a6f0c28-bf9a-4b78-95ae-2fa1f0fca60d.JPG"], "crew203Definition": "Crew 203\nCrew 203 is a seismic field crew operating mainly in onshore Libya.\nIts main tasks include conducting 3D seismic surveys, collecting subsurface data, and operating seismic equipment like vibroseis and drilling systems.", "crew206Definition": "Crew 206 is another seismic field crew in NAGECO with similar responsibilities.\nIt performs seismic surveys, operates modern equipment, and works in different locations depending on project assignments.", "hiveChartImageUrl": "/uploads/1773828995807-ad7e0432-2362-42cb-a51e-53cab0af016a.png", "heroCarouselImages": ["/uploads/1773139755861-7cd9a7db-7700-4e26-98b6-944b93150734.JPG", "/uploads/1773139713624-ff21e565-3686-43f4-9fe4-0c00a7a8ccc7.JPG", "/uploads/